metadata.name: MD X Partner
metadata.description:
MD X is an eXperimental media hub backed by IT science. We connect the experts that share our vision to reinvent marketing and advertising in Web3. We onboard impactful brands and help them turn their consumers into communities engaging them as co-creators in a new era of WebX.

This token will give you access to the private partner channel where we will shape the Web3 vision and synergize for exciting projects.
